### Optional CI extras

- Lighthouse CI budgets on critical routes (document thresholds in repo).

## Acceptance Criteria

- All changed files pass the linter and formatter before commit.
- Type-check passes on the changed module.
- Pre-commit hooks are not bypassed without documented reason.
